												"value": "<p>Liferay’s Digital Asset Management (DAM) tools simplify the organization and management of digital assets. Assets include images, videos, presentations, documents, and much more. <p>Additionally, the Asset Library feature enables you to manage and publish assets in one central repository for use across multiple distinct sites.<div>Check these articles for an introduction:<ul><li><a href=/w/dxp/content-authoring-and-management/asset-libraries>Asset Libraries</a><li><a href=/w/dxp/content-authoring-and-management/documents-and-media>Documents and Media</a><li><a href=/w/dxp/content-authoring-and-management/documents-and-media/uploading-and-managing/uploading-files>Uploading Files</a><li><a href=/w/dxp/system-administration/file-storage>File Storage</a><li><a href=/w/dxp/content-authoring-and-management/documents-and-media/publishing-and-sharing/using-adaptive-media>Using Adaptive Media</a><li><a href=/web/guest/w/dxp/content-authoring-and-management/documents-and-media/uploading-and-managing/managing-metadata/defining-document-types>Defining Document Types</a></ul></div>"
